        <mxCell id="flowNote" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=13;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" value="Primary runtime flow:&lt;br&gt;1. URL versioning selects v1/v2; v1 emits Deprecation + Sunset&lt;br&gt;2. Swagger publishes concrete versioned contracts&lt;br&gt;3. Controllers delegate to services; all errors use Problem Details&lt;br&gt;4. Repositories query/save through NotificationDbContext&lt;br&gt;5. Bulk admission is atomic/bounded; terminal jobs release payloads&lt;br&gt;6. BulkNotificationWorker processes jobs through scoped services&lt;br&gt;7. Disabled email returns NotAttempted and leaves the persisted intent pending" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="690" x="370" y="960" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
